title: VU project to secure patient privacy will lead to improved medical research (Victoria University)
text: ( Source : Victoria University ) Wed 21 October 2015 Patient privacy will be at the forefront of a new electronic data system being developed at Victoria University that will eliminate internal privacy breaches in medical research. Victoria
